Cali Photo Dump 😝 I am so glad I finally made it out to California again after 5 years of saying “i’m coming frfr” 🤣 I forced myself to take this trip to get back to living life again and to get back to some kind of “normal” in my life after the heartbreaking year i just had. I NEEEDED to be with friends I haven’t seen in so long and friends i’ve been wanting to meet for a while! Every hug from every single one of you really helped heal me little by little and thank yall for the love, memories, the laughter, the CRAZYNESS and the foooooood ❤️ theres so much more I wanted to do, so much more i needed to see and tons more people i needed to meet but I promise i’ll be back! LA you may have my ego but San Diego has my soul 🤣❤️😘 i love you friends frfr thank you. See you again soon! Oh…i ain’t tagging everyone yall know who you are! 🤣
I think I found my true calling in being an announcer or commentator 🤣 it’s the narration for me 🤦🏻‍♂️

Last time I was on a plane was Aug 2019. It felt good traveling again after the rough couple years. ❤️ I miss you Cali 😭 i’ll be back soon! 😘

#travel #travelvlog #delta #flight #vacation

I literally ATE my way through my 10 day trip to California 🤣 I gained a few lbs but it was all worth it for the deliciousness my friends showed me! 🤤 there is still so much more I wanted to taste which means i’ll just have to come back soon! 😘
